  "text": "3 https://github.com/mcdm/CommitmentBank/ Discourse relation prediction has been used by [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] for sentence representation learning evaluation, but the dataset they use (PDTB [CITATION_3] ) is included in ours.",
